<html>
  <head>
    <title>Request for Verification of Employment Reference</title>
    {{> styles}}
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="norland-msg">
      <div class="norland-space-top">
        <p>Dear {{clientName}},</p>

        <p>I am reaching out on behalf of Norland Agency. We are currently assisting {{nannyFirstName}} {{nannyLastName}} in securing a new position. As part of our standard process, we are seeking to confirm the details of the reference they have provided regarding their period of employment with you.</p>

        <p>Please click the 'Verify Reference' button below to review and confirm the details of the reference.</p>

        <a href={{returnUrl}} class="norland-button norland-space-top" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Verify Reference</a>

        <p>If you have any additional comments or concerns regarding {{nannyFirstName}}'s performance or employment history, please do not hesitate to share them with me directly.</p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>Norland Agency</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>